#### 5.2.4 Cycle Management

**Cycle fields:**
- Cycle name (e.g., "BPC-157 healing cycle Q1 2026")
- Start date and optional end date (or "ongoing")
- Associated protocols (multiple protocols can be linked to one cycle)
